title: BIP 21: Badger/DIGG Emission Plan Part 1
body:
TLDR; Overview structure and plan for badger/digg emissions.

Approval to ratify the results of the polls within the BIP summarized below:
1) Badger LP + Staking ratio at 39%
2) Badger LP Share compared to Staking, Yes to framework for Badger and DIGG
3) Uniswap LP vs Sushiswap LP split: 50/50 emissions
4) Implementation and approval of Dynamics Emissions Model dual token distribution and Agree to apply framework prior to DIGG launch: Yes

See discussion: https://forum.badger.finance/t/bip-21-badger-digg-emission-plan-part-i/1692
author: 0xa001B5639e4ed26dF58367016eB08850e3e55655
